headline: How Sempra’s 2025 Earnings Guidance Update and Growth Outlook Have Changed Its Investment Story (SRE)
summary: Sempra recently updated its full-year 2025 earnings guidance to a range of US$3.29 to US$3.69 per share under GAAP and reaffirmed its commitment to a high-end growth rate outlook during its Value Creation Update Call on September 23, 2025, followed by presentations at the Wolfe Research Utilities, Midstream & Clean Energy Conference in New York.
